            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1626433110426-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crumble your<strong> feta</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>crumbled feta cheese</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to a large bowl and set aside</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1626433114628-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1626433114628-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1626433114628-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
