            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked bulgur</strong> and <strong>warmed grapes </strong>to the bowl with the salad and give everything a good mix – this is your <strong>fruity feta salad</strong></p>",
